WEBVTT

00:00:02.460 --> 00:00:05.093
(Music: "La Vie en Rose")

00:00:15.681 --> 00:00:19.519
Cecily: Ah, well,
I feel rather frightened.

00:00:19.543 --> 00:00:22.385
I'm so afraid he will look
just like everyone else.

00:00:22.409 --> 00:00:23.861
(Algernon sniffs)

00:00:26.718 --> 00:00:27.869
C: He does.

00:00:27.893 --> 00:00:31.234
Algernon: You are my little
cousin Cecily, I'm sure.